        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei aeterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Omnibus sanctae Dei Ecclesiae fidelibus
                        nostrisque presentibus scilicet et futuris notum esse volumus, qualiter
                            <persName key="#Intercessory #Bishops" ref="#people/123"
                            >Adelardus</persName> et <persName key="#Intercessory #Bishops"><name
                                ref="Antonius">Antonius</name></persName> venerabiles <rs
                            key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> atque <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Marquis/duke"><name ref="UUaldefredus"
                                >Vualfredus</name></persName> illuster <rs key="#Marquis/duke"
                            >marchio</rs> nostri dilectissimi <rs key="#fidelisOf">fideles</rs>
                        nostram humiliter postulaverunt <rs key="#Intercessory">clementiam</rs>,
                        quatenus <persName key="#Queen" ref="#people/55">Angilbergae</persName>
                        serenissimae <rs key="#Queen">imperatrici</rs> concedere et confirmare
                        nostrae auctoritatis precepto dignaremur quandam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/82"><rs key="#Monasteries">abbatiam</rs> in
                            honore apostolorum principis dicatam</orgName> et non longe ab urbe
                            <placeName ref="#places/43">Placentina</placeName> fundatam in loco
                        nuncupato <placeName ref="#places/14">Caput Trebie</placeName>, seu etiam
                        quasdam <rs key="#Curtes">cortes</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/40">Vuardistallam</geogName> videlicet, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/38">Luciariam</geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/77">Litora Palludiana</geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/110">Campum Miliacium</geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/112">Sextum</geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/113">Iverne</geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/114">Massini</geogName> atque <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#estates/115">Leocarni</geogName> quemadmodum domnus <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/110">Hludovicus</persName> gloriosus
                        olim <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> avunculus et senior noster eidem
                        imperatrici per suorum preceptorum paginas concessit atque perdonavit.
                        Quorum precibus inflexi prenominatam abbatiam atque <rs key="#Royal_slave"
                            >familiis utriusque sexus</rs> seu etiam <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >quae dici aut nominari possunt per diversa nostri regni loca ad
                            pretaxatam abbatiam vel ad easdem cortes pertinentibus in integrum</rs>,
                        veluti prelibatus serenissimus imperator Hludovicus et quondam noster
                        avunculus nosterque carissimus senior <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/32">Karolus</persName> videlicet invictissimus imperator
                        per preceptorum suorum auctoritatem iam saepe nominatae Angilbergae
                        gloriosae imperatrici tribuerunt ac confirmaverunt. Nec non et omnia quae in
                        aliis preceptis tam sibi quamque <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> in
                        honore <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/53">sancti Sixti
                            dicato</orgName> et ab ipsa infra civitatem Placentinam constructo ab
                        aliis nostris antecessoribus donata et corroborata fuisse noscuntur. Nos ob
                        Dei amorem tam ad utilitatem ipsius Angilbergae imperatricis quamque ad usus
                        et alimenta <rs key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales">monacharum</rs> quae pro tempore
                        in eodem monasterio Christo domino servierint de nostro iure et dominio in
                        ipsius Angilbergae excellentissimae imperatricis et monasterii ius et
                        dominium usque <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">in
                            perpetuum iure peroprietario</rs> concedimus ac perdonamus, modisque
                        omnibus confirmamus et conroboramus per hanc nostrae inscriptionis paginam
                        una cum <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >casis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terris</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Wine #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >campis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >pascuis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >silvis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >salectis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Ports"
                            >sationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >aquis aquarumque decursibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >molendinis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >piscationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">servis et
                            ancillis</rs>, <rs key="#Aldius">aldionibus et aldianis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Mountains #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >montibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Natural_landscape #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >vallibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Natural_landscape #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >planiciebus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >coltis et incoltis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">divisis et
                            indivisis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Natural_landscape #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >ripis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >rupunis</rs>, <rs key="#Levies #Public_exactions">vestigalibus,
                            districtionibus, reddibitionibus</rs> universisque ad predictam abbatiam
                        vel iam nominatas cortes pertinentibus vel aspicientibus ex integro,
                        quatenus ipsa, quoad vixerit, eandem abbatiam et pretaxatas cortes
                        potestative teneat ac possideat et ordinet, totius potestatis contradictione
                        remota. Quicumque ergo hoc nostrae concessionis et confirmationis preceptum
                        infringere vel violare quandoque temptaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri obtimi libras centum sexaginta</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem palacii nostri camerae</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera">medietatem cui inuste facta fuerit molestia</rs>. Quod
                        autem ut verius credatur et diligentius ab omnibus perpetualiter observetur,
                        manu propria roboantes de anulo nostro subter insigniri iussimus. Signum
                        domni Berengarii serenissimi regis. <persName key="#Chancellor"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/123">Adelardi</persName>
                        episcopi et <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et
                        subscripsi. Data VIII id. mai(i), anno incarnationis Domini DCCCLXXXVIII,
                        domni autem Berengarii gloriosissimi regis I, indictione VI actum Papie. In
                        Dei nomine feliciter amen.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
